{"id": 571, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在什么情况下会觉得别人喜欢你？", "description": "啊，生活！将我逼上了在不解风情和自作多情中摇摆的不归路！", "record_count": 7763, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194333CRJrnDtN73AgFjT4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-14T11:32:47Z", "options": [{"id": 16896, "content": "有钱的情况下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246260}, {"id": 17664, "content": "爱我我爱的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254967}, {"id": 17153, "content": "叫我起床吃早饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217917}, {"id": 16898, "content": "“吃饭吗！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 17154, "content": "发自拍的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195048}, {"id": 17410, "content": "会一直盯着你看，眼神温柔", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253318}, {"id": 17411, "content": "堕入爱河", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251173}, {"id": 16901, "content": "没有任何时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250291}, {"id": 26629, "content": "隐身对其可见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 315585}, {"id": 16902, "content": "和我说话的异性（除了我爸）一定都是喜欢我的", "image": "img/option/option/20160606144816hyxSw5FLAsdPG6l7.jpg", "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246421}, {"id": 17158, "content": "双方都能感受到暧昧的动作", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223649}, {"id": 17414, "content": "做决定前会先问问我的意见", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253287}, {"id": 18182, "content": "偷偷看你多次秒你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181992}, {"id": 16903, "content": "行动和语言同步", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250319}, {"id": 17415, "content": "在我无奈独自旅行的时候他决定陪我", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252597}, {"id": 16904, "content": "带我吃好吃的，给我买好吃的，带我给我去买好吃的。不是只会说你在干嘛！而且，你等我去接你！或者，带我去玩好玩的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250333}, {"id": 18184, "content": "看见他就想啪啪啪！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258051}, {"id": 16905, "content": "看我的眼神，说话的语气，都会变得很温柔", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250326}, {"id": 16906, "content": "他一直都喜欢我???", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250337}, {"id": 16907, "content": "在干嘛阿、？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 48636}, {"id": 17419, "content": "因为你可以很开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 226798}, {"id": 16908, "content": "在幻想的时候?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 95793}, {"id": 17164, "content": "快到情人节了，她跟我说，又要一个人过了，同时表示不想一个人过。。。我以为。。然并卵。。想多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223231}, {"id": 16909, "content": "说话的时候很小心", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250357}, {"id": 17933, "content": "把我思考进他的生活里、", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254540}, {"id": 16910, "content": "我看她的时候正好她也看过来", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235437}, {"id": 18446, "content": "转的星座内容除了他自己的还有我的（当然可能不是为了我）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259113}, {"id": 16911, "content": "应该是 就算那天没怎么说话 还是会说早安 和 晚安 的时候吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250362}, {"id": 16912, "content": "常问你在干嘛啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 249150}, {"id": 17424, "content": "对你比别人都好但是就不说我爱你", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253380}, {"id": 16913, "content": "会主动关心我", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194834}, {"id": 16914, "content": "怎么会有人不喜欢我", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193135}, {"id": 16915, "content": "我所有的朋友圈秒赞，我所有的微信秒回", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200751GtTfWLxrhpkY4mOJ.jpg", "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169698}, {"id": 16916, "content": "  感觉那个人突然对自己好了起来！", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241123}, {"id": 16920, "content": "看我看我看我……还是看我……", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250419}, {"id": 17432, "content": "什么事都想着我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253406}, {"id": 17433, "content": "会主动关心我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253411}, {"id": 16922, "content": "看到对方就不好意思地低头", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139949}, {"id": 17178, "content": "出门见他是洗了头发的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241975}, {"id": 17435, "content": "告诉我，他喜欢我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253451}, {"id": 16924, "content": "帮你拨头发", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250476}, {"id": 16925, "content": "不可能有人喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225511}, {"id": 17693, "content": "我想伸手抱她的时候，她已经笑着扑到了我怀里。想听下文吗，我还能编?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255130}, {"id": 18461, "content": "愿意跟我聊天，不管我的话题有多无聊和鸡毛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259241}, {"id": 16927, "content": "他给我点赞了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 200853}, {"id": 17185, "content": "我是那种就算别人直白的说出我喜欢你时 我都不会百分百相信他真的喜欢我………", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252136}, {"id": 17441, "content": "不再赞美我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219807}, {"id": 18721, "content": "除了父母，没人会一直喜欢你，所谓的喜欢只是一时兴起好感而已，所谓的喜欢也就是这兴起时间的长短罢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259031}, {"id": 20513, "content": "给别人发红包的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177998}, {"id": 16931, "content": "不要脸的时候哈哈哈 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250504}]}